sql:
SELECT AVG(average_monthly_transaction_amount) AS avg_monthly_transaction
FROM financial_behavior
WHERE valid_risk_assessment_ind = 1;

SELECT customer_id, average_monthly_transaction_amount
FROM financial_behavior
WHERE valid_risk_assessment_ind = 1;

external_knowledge:
Valid risk assessment means that the customer has completed a risk assessment and it has been validated by the financial institution; 
An investor is someone who invests in financial products;
Interest in financial management products is determined by the customer's preferences or past investments in such products.
